# Can.IA Design Specification Document

_Complete design system documentation for Figma recreation_

## Overview

Can.IA is a modern AI agents platform with a clean, professional design emphasizing trust, efficiency, and technological sophistication. The design uses a minimal color palette with strategic use of accent colors to highlight key information.

