### Colors

#### Light Theme

```
Primary Colors:
- Primary: #030213 (Dark navy - main brand color)
- Primary Foreground: #ffffff (White text on primary)
- Background: #ffffff (Page background)
- Foreground: oklch(0.145 0 0) (Main text color - very dark gray)

Secondary Colors:
- Secondary: oklch(0.95 0.0058 264.53) (Very light purple-gray)
