### Typography

#### Font System

- Base Font Size: 16px
- Font Weight Normal: 400
- Font Weight Medium: 500
- Line Height: 1.5 (for all text elements)

#### Type Scale

```
Headings:
- H1: text-2xl (24px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5
- H2: text-xl (20px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5
- H3: text-lg (18px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5
- H4: text-base (16px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5

Body Text:
- Paragraph: text-base (16px), font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.5
- Small: text-sm (14px), font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.5

Interactive Elements:
- Button: text-base (16px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5
- Label: text-base (16px), font-weight: 500, line-height: 1.5
- Input: text-base (16px), font-weight: 400, line-height: 1.5
```

#### Hero Typography (Special Cases)

```
- Hero H1: text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl (36px/60px/72px)
- Hero Subtitle: text-lg md:text-xl (18px/20px)
- Section Headers: text-3xl md:text-4xl (30px/36px)
```

### Spacing & Layout

#### Spacing Scale

```
- Space 1: 4px (0.25rem)
- Space 2: 8px (0.5rem)
- Space 3: 12px (0.75rem)
- Space 4: 16px (1rem)
- Space 6: 24px (1.5rem)
- Space 8: 32px (2rem)
- Space 12: 48px (3rem)
- Space 16: 64px (4rem)
- Space 20: 80px (5rem)
```

#### Border Radius

```
- Radius SM: calc(var(--radius) - 4px) ‚âà 6px
- Radius MD: calc(var(--radius) - 2px) ‚âà 8px
- Radius LG: var(--radius) = 10px (0.625rem)
- Radius XL: calc(var(--radius) + 4px) ‚âà 14px
```

#### Container & Grid

```
- Max Width: 1152px (6xl)
- Container Padding: 24px (1.5rem) on mobile, 24px on desktop
- Grid Columns: 1 (mobile), 2 (tablet), 3-4 (desktop)
- Grid Gap: 32px (2rem)
```

