## üé® Visual Guidelines

### Gradients

- Hero text gradient: linear, 180¬∞, from foreground (0%) to muted-foreground (100%)
- CTA background: linear, 90¬∞, from primary/10 (0%) via primary/5 (50%) to primary/10 (100%)

### Shadows

- Card hover: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)
- Demo card: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)

### Overlays

- Demo card gradient: linear, 0¬∞, from background (0%) via transparent (50%) to transparent (100%)
- Background sections: muted with 50% opacity

### Animations

- All transitions: 200ms ease-in-out
- Hover effects: scale 1.02 on cards
- Button hovers: slight opacity change (90%)

